                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#93va">Fol. 93va</locus>-vb: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 93va-vb: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘደብረ፡ ቂርቆስ፡ ኡራ፡ ሕፃን፡ ዘአጥረያ፡ በንዋ[ዩ]፡ ከመ፡ ትኩኖ፡ መርሃ፡ ውስተ፡ መንግሥተ፡ ሰማይ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ አነ፡ ጸሐፊሃ፡ ዘሚካኤል፡ ኢትርስዑኒ፡ በሞትየ፡ ወሕይወትየ፡ ፩አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note mentions ʿUra Däbrä Qirqos as the owning institution and Zä-Mikaʾel as the scribe.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#93vb">Fols. 93vb-94</locus>ra: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 93vb-94ra: ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘአጽሐፋ፡ ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ በወርቁ፡ ወወሀባ፡ ለደብረ፡ ቂርቆስ፡ ዖራ፡ ወደቂቁ፡ አምደ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ገረድ፡ ወደቂቀ፡ አምደ፡ ኪካኤል[sic]፡ ኹዕላይ፡ {ወአዶንያስ}፡ ወደበሳይ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖሙ፡ መርሃ፡ ለመንግ[ስ]ተ፡ ሰማያት።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note has been written in red ink.
It mentions the name Wäldä Giyorgis as the commissioner.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title of the work is crudely written in black paint on the outer face of the front board.&#xD;
- The name Gabrä Ḥǝ[y]wät is written by pencil on fol. 1v.&#xD;
- Words ʾǝgäle and ʾǝgälit are marked by thin lines above and below: e.g., fols. 13vb, 38rb, 41rb, 78ra.&#xD;
- Corrections written interlineally: fols. 31rb, 60va, 75va.&#xD;
- Correction written in the upper margin: fol. 89v.</item>
                     </list>
